{"tid":2382633,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BTS所屬事務所向YG子公司投資近5億","createTime":"2021-01-27T11:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T12:55:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9bc583a592fc787a6384507aa38431085b7bdf","tid":2382633,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"韓國演藝界兩大巨頭YG事務所和Big Hit事務所破天荒合作，根據今日韓媒報道，旗下擁有紅爆全球的男團防彈少年團（BTS）的Big Hit及其子公司beNX一起向YG子公司YG Plus投資700億韓圜（約4.9億港元），三間公司將會通過今次投資奠定了合作的基礎，並會開展各種業務的合作。<br />\n<br />\n今日召開董事會<br />\n報道指Big Hit今日召開董事會，最終決定今次合作事宜，當中YG Plus的藝人全球相關事業將會通過beNX的「Weverse」展開，而YG Plus亦會參與Big Hit的唱片、音源等事業，同時亦計劃擴張fans的平台事業。YG Plus方面表示：「在各自的領域上一直追求最高地位的兩家公司合作，創造了新的轉機。」Big Hit方面亦表示：「期待與多個事業及領域擁有強大網絡的YG Plus合作，大家透過各種合作而共同成長。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c2PHKo2l_9Z1-MuToOpChQ0-_4w=/802x905/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RC7AYUTQ4VEGNFK7X7ENIEEG2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fc2PHKo2l_9Z1-MuToOpChQ0-_4w%3D%2F802x905%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRC7AYUTQ4VEGNFK7X7ENIEEG2Y.jpg&h=34f310d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92594774eb66f8b4683ee51f5c07d8edc000efb3","tid":2382633,"uid":307927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"Big hit得BTS都唔支持得耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13409d1d357f36d915fcc6be2c16cb5a4ee1d7a","tid":2382633,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T11:58:52.000Z","msg":"YG既音樂+BTS<br />\n即係強化版BIGBANG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841a37c34e156ede735df672c33d2f067fe79bd5","tid":2382633,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:22:14.000Z","msg":"=<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a4c44b4a3e4e21b2ddd43485695af794248a7d","tid":2382633,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:55:46.000Z","msg":"反攻YG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}